        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: immunogold-silver particles are observed (arrows) in membranes of parallel fiber synaptic terminals\n\n5/12/2016 Pim\n- integral component in the annotation is derived from TM-domains in the annotated protein.\n- Literal Fig1 \"Many immunogold-silver particles are observed (arrows) in membranes of parallel fiber synaptic terminals (PFT in a-d) making asymmetrical synapses with immunonegative Purkinje cell dendritic spines (sp).\". Experimental description: Results: \"Fig. 1 Subcellular compartmentalization of Kv3.1b in the **rat** cerebellar molecular layer.\"" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099056 replaced by GO:0042734" ;
